item.title: Dikto
item.description: A dictionary website built using Angular. It uses external APIs from Wordnik, Merriam-Webster, and Google Translate API.

item.title: TOEIC Web System
item.description: A system where Japanese TOEIC-exam takers can study, review, and take quizzes to prepare for their exams.

item.title: About
item.description: I’m a self-taught developer who specializes in web development using modern javascript libraries and frameworks like Angular 2, React, and Node JS. I have also dabbled in other languages such as Go, Java, PHP, and C#. I am currently working with a young and driven team in creating a mobile game. In recent projects I have been a part of, I usually handle server-side stuff and architecture planning + design.
